      "text": "sult of the PRLI Request and the status of the image pair.  The meanings of the encoded Re-",
      "bbox": [
        122.4,
        69.65,
        539.98,
        80.76
      ],
      "block_index": 3,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
