        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0013",
      "text": "Request Node Identification Data (RNID)",
      "bbox": [
        133.82,
        358.96,
        324.24,
        370.08
      ],
      "block_index": 6,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0014",
      "text": "4.2.23.1  Introduction",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        382.96,
        195.92,
        394.08
      ],
      "block_index": 7,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0015",
      "text": "The RNID ELS is an ELS for acquiring Node Identification Data.  The normal response shall be an",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        406.96,
        539.92,
        418.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0016",
      "text": "Accept (ACC) ELS Sequence with Node Identification Data in its payload.  If the recipient Nx_Port or",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        418.96,
        540.08,
        430.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0017",
      "text": "Fx_Port does not support the RNID ELS, it shall reply with an LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a reason",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        430.96,
        540.04,
        442.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0018",
      "text": "code of \"Command not supported\".  If the recipient Nx_Port or Fx_Port does not support the request-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        442.96,
        540.02,
        454.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0019",
      "text": "ed Node Identification Data format, it shall either reply with an LS_RJT ELS Sequence with a reason",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        454.96,
        540.01,
        466.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0020",
      "text": "code of \"Unable to perform command request\" and reason code explanation of \"Unable to supply re-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        466.96,
        540.08,
        478.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0021",
      "text": "quested data\" or reply with an Accept ELS Payload containing only the Common Identification Data.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        478.96,
        536.89,
        490.08
      ],
      "block_index": 8,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0022",
      "text": "If an Nx_Port sends an RNID ELS and receives an LS_RJT Sequence with a reason code of \"Unable",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        502.96,
        540.0,
        514.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0023",
      "text": "to perform command request\" and reason code explanation of \"Unable to supply requested data\", the",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        514.96,
        539.99,
        526.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0024",
      "text": "ULP may cause the Nx_Port to retry the RNID ELS with a different Node Identification Data Format",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        526.96,
        540.01,
        538.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0025",
      "text": "request if an Nx_Port sends an RNID ELS and receives a reply with an Accept ELS containing only",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        538.96,
        540.01,
        550.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0026",
      "text": "Common Identification Data (see Table 61) in its payload, the ULP usage of the Common Identifica-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        550.96,
        540.08,
        562.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0027",
      "text": "tion Data and any further discovery processing is beyond the scope of this standard.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        562.96,
        467.76,
        574.08
      ],
      "block_index": 9,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0028",
      "text": "The RNID ELS may be sent to any Nx_Port or Fx_Port in the Fabric.  If the destination is known to be",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        586.96,
        540.04,
        598.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0029",
      "text": "an Fx_Port, then the RNID ELS shall be sent to the Fabric Controller (FFFFFDh).  If an RNID ELS is",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        598.96,
        540.03,
        610.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0030",
      "text": "sent to the Fabric Controller (FFFFFDh), the reply shall represent the Fabric Controller node that",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        610.96,
        539.93,
        622.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0031",
      "text": "contains the Fx_Port to which the requesting FC port is attached.  If the receiving FC port has been",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        622.96,
        539.96,
        634.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p082_s0032",
      "text": "determined to be an Nx_Port, then the RNID ELS shall be sent to that Nx_Port.",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        634.96,
        445.51,
        646.08
      ],
      "block_index": 10,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
